VALUES (386, 'Depth Jump to Broad Jump Video Exercise Guide', 'Quads', 'Plyometrics', 'Box', 'Compound',
        'Push (Bilateral)', 'Advanced', 'Abs, Adductors, Calves, Glutes, Hamstrings, Hip Flexors', 'The depth jump to broad jump is a variation of the box jump and an exercise used to increase lower body explosiveness.
